Any suggestion how can I implement tabs support with crispy forms for translated fields?
I can do it explicitly by define helper.layout and combine fields with TabHolder
```
class CourseForm(forms.ModelForm):

    @property
    def helper(self):
        helper = FormHelper()
        helper.layout = Layout(...)
```

But maybe I can do it programmatically? (some way override fields list and there widgets? Where should I do it?)

##### Issue description
When I do
`pipenv install git+git@github.com/requests/requests.git#egg=requests` 
(yes I know the URL is malformed), pipenv fails with `UnboundLocalError`.

##### Expected result

An error message saying the URL is malformed.

##### Actual result
```
Installing git+git@github.com/requests/requests.git#egg=requests…
